## How to Use\line
1) Choose Mode — Standard | Qual | Lite  \line
2) Fill **STAR** (one screen)  \line
3) Complete **A** and lock **A.4** (3–5 criteria)  \line
4) Do **R**; include ≥1 killed decision gate  \line
5) Report **C.1**; assess **C.2**; decide **C.3**  \line
6) Add the compliance footer (license, accessibility, last updated)\line
\line
**Status vocabulary**: Quant → `Pass | Partial | Fail` • Qual → `Supported | Mixed | Not Supported | Emergent`  \line
**Reliability target**: κ/α ≥ 0.70 where applicable.  \line
**Data sources**: `system_log:<table>/<field>`, `instrument:<tool>@<version>`.  \line
**Style**: SI units; ISO dates.\line
\line
